<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<h2>Introduction</h2>
<p>Thank you for visiting our website. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal data is handled in a safe and responsible manner. This Privacy Policy outlines the types of information we collect, how we use it, and the measures we take to protect your information.</p>

<h2>Data Collection</h2>
<h3>Information We Collect</h3>
<p>We collect only the necessary data required for providing our services, specifically when you choose to register or log in using your Spotify account. The types of information we may collect include:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Spotify Account Information:</strong> This includes your Spotify username, email address, and other profile information as permitted by Spotify's API.</li>
</ul>

<h3>No Data Collection for General Browsing</h3>
<p>If you are merely browsing our website without logging in or registering, we do not collect any personal information from you.</p>

<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>The information we collect from your Spotify account is used solely for the following purposes:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Account Management:</strong> To create and manage your user account on our website.</li>
    <li><strong>Service Delivery:</strong> To provide personalized features and services based on your Spotify profile.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Data Storage and Security</h2>
<p>We take the security of your personal data seriously and implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure.</p>

<h3>Data Retention</h3>
<p>We retain your personal information only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy or as required by law. If you delete your account, we will delete your personal data from our systems.</p>

<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
<p>We do not share your personal data with third parties except as necessary to provide our services or as required by law. Our website integrates with Spotify’s API to facilitate user login and profile access. Your use of Spotify’s login service is subject to Spotify’s privacy policy.</p>

<h2>Your Rights</h2>
<p>You have the right to:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Access Your Data:</strong> Request a copy of the personal data we hold about you.</li>
    <li><strong>Correct Your Data:</strong> Request that we correct any inaccurate or incomplete information.</li>
    <li><strong>Delete Your Data:</strong> Request the deletion of your personal data, subject to certain conditions.</li>
    <li><strong>Object to Processing:</strong> Object to our processing of your personal data under certain circumstances.</li>
</ul>
<p>To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at [your contact email].</p>

